      protected VersionsReportRendererBase(org.apache.maven.doxia.sink.Sink sink, org.codehaus.plexus.i18n.I18N i18n, Locale locale, String bundleName, boolean allowSnapshots)
      Creates a new report renderer instance.
      Parameters:
      sink - the sink to render to, must not be null
      i18n - the i18n component, must not be null
      locale - the locale we are rendering for, must not be null
      bundleName - the name of the resource bundle to use, must not be null
      allowSnapshots - whether snapshots should be included
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if any of the parameters are null
